{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_28","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated `library-new-request` job for `org.apache.camel:camel-health:4.20.0` failed, although preserved follow-up work is available on the branch below:\nhttps://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-4803-library-new-request-org.apache.camel-camel-health-4.20.0-6ab13492\n\nThe most likely failing stage was generated-test stabilization/finalization, not artifact discovery. The generated tests failed repeatedly during `gradle-test`: early JVM runs hit `org.apache.camel.NoSuchLanguageException: No language could be found for: simple` in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:camel-health:4.20.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-28T07-25-25-143186Z.log` and `...07-32-24-093293Z.log`, and later native runs still failed in `defaultLoaderDiscoversClasspathHealthChecksFromCamelServiceDescriptors()` and `registryRegistersDirectChecksRepositoriesAndAppliesLookupAndExclusionRules()` in `.../gradle-test-2026-06-28T07-29-11-637200Z.log` and `.../gradle-test-2026-06-28T07-42-50-700830Z.log`.\n\nThe preserved branch contains additional human-intervention work beyond the recorded `ending_commit`: it adds `metadata/org.apache.camel/camel-health/4.20.0/reachability-metadata.json`, updates the generated test, and records a post-gen intervention. Local validation then turns green: `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:camel-health:4.20.0/post-gen/pi-post-gen-2026-06-28T07-43-40-762871Z.log` reports `BUILD SUCCESSFUL` with `7` native tests passing, and the final reruns in `.../gradle-test-2026-06-28T07-45-18-198491Z.log`, `...07-45-29-272343Z.log`, and `...07-45-58-939037Z.log` all show `Test for org.apache.camel:camel-health:4.20.0 passed.`\n\nThe remaining problem appears to be workflow bookkeeping/finalization. `stats/org.apache.camel/camel-health/4.20.0/execution-metrics.json` still records `status: failure`,